Package: extractoR
Title: Self-Correcting Structured Extraction with LLMs in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Skander Tahar", "Mulder", , email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Skander Tahar Mulder <your.email@example.com>
Maintainer: Skander Tahar Mulder <your.email@example.com>
Description: Like Python's 'instructor' or 'outlines'. Automatically retries LLM calls
    with validation feedback until output matches your schema. Uses ellmer for LLM
    interface and jsonvalidate for schema validation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
